➜Geek之王Linus Torvalds
https://www.solidot.org/story?sid=28819	32400
《连线》<a href="http://www.wired.com/wiredenterprise/2012/03/mr-linux/all/1">采访了Linux创始人Linus Torvalds</a>。<i>
